# Target modern browsers only - no legacy support needed
# This significantly reduces bundle size by avoiding unnecessary polyfills

# Support browsers with >1% global usage that support ES2022 features
defaults and supports es6-module
not dead
not op_mini all
not ie > 0
not and_uc > 0

# Explicitly support recent versions of major browsers (last 2 years)
Chrome >= 100
Firefox >= 100
Safari >= 15.4
Edge >= 100